Xegony <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ualiannasedai.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alianna Sedai</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/8/01 6:08:20 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Yes, you can fix PoG factions</span><hr size=1> You need to have a friendly high level Enchanter charm Pandos in Freeport, and give him bazillions of muffins.<br>
