-Alianna Sedai <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukeanar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Keanar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/8/01 12:02:55 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoG faction and epic</span><hr size=1> ive been waiting and wondering about this myself<br>
