<br>
1st off, a charmed mob doesn't give faction hits when you do a quest, so muffins dont work...<br>
<br>
second off, the faction (from my exp... turned in 3000+ bat wings and kinda turned in muffins a sorta exploit way, ench charms mob, i open the trade window, ench invises me, then camps, then i hit trade, and get the faction... turned in a good 1000 muffins this way and was still scowl to all factions you take hits from in pog... <br>
<br>
well the only solution was alot of multi questing... <br>
<br>
a pog hunting druid is kos to the following mobs for our epic... 2 of which are level 60 and can't be charmed, period, heh... <br>
<br>
Athele,<br>
Foloal<br>
Pained Unicorn... <br>
<br>
Athele and the Unicorn cann't be charmed... so here is how i did my epic... <br>
<br>
a very good friend of mine did all the quest up to the hardened mixture, i did the rune crested bowl quest, he turned in the mixture, i turned in the bowl second, i got the stone... <br>
<br>
then another very good friend did all the of cleansed spirit of faydwer quest for me, to multi quest with me once the quest was down to turning everything in to Xanatuus... <br>
<br>
Foloal is is charmable with dictate so once i got my vs stone i had an enchanter freind charm her and i turned in my vs stone and sftly glowing stone for the warmly pulsating stone (i think?) for my elab scimitar i wasn't kos to any other mob in the quest... well cept for the Faelia Bloodbriar, which is why the ranger friend had to do all of the quest up to the hardened mix (also scince athele is kos to me =x) <br>
<br>
anyway, in the end my friend turned in the cleansed spirit of faydwer and i turned in the scim, kunark, and antonica... and i got my epic... took forever and you have to have alot of friends willing to help you.. but its doable =) <p><center>
<i>"Every man I meet is my superior in some way. In that, I learn of him" -- Emerson</i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uteenawarmheart.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Teena Warmheart</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/8/01 2:09:09 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoG faction and epic</span><hr size=1> It seems that it will only be doable until Verant figures out how to stop multi-questing. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/upotatofarmer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>potatofarmer</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/11/01 1:57:58 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoG faction and epic</span><hr size=1> hehe for your info and anyone else it took about 5000 muffins to go from scowl to dubious... hehe i figured out the same little exploit as you, and used a chanter friend on a second puter.  i cant even explain how annoying and how long it took to turn in 5000 muffins 16 at a time using that exploit....... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uaandaie.showPublicProfile?language=EN>aandaie</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/11/01 4:42:14 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://home.dencity.com/aandaie/aand.jpg height=60 width=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> I would not reccomend this but...</span><hr size=1> <br>
