<br>
*First of all I am 56 human druid, wasnt using wolfform, and the muffin guy was way green* At the end of the hallway from Muffin Dorf(cant think of his name).  I cast harmony on him and slowly moved up to him with muffins in hand til the trade window opened. I had enough time to drop 4 muffins in each trade slot (16 muffins total) pressed trade and quickly backed up. Got the faction for each. I did this til I was dubious, at which point I just sat in front of him and did the quest normally. <br>
<br>
Overall it only took me 2 and a half hours to go from KOS to Ally with the unicorn.<br>
<br>
Personally this seems easier than troubling some poor enchanter =P<br>
<br>
Hope this works for all of you.<br>
